{"tid":2008061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍東同港島都有都有特訓Channel 啦","createTime":"2020-05-08T17:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T17:56:58.000Z","uid":200786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a4fb09df67faeffa1ff0076394256726fa17a614","tid":2008061,"uid":200786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:45:55.000Z","msg":"九龍東<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CiZwLuB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCiZwLuB.jpg&h=b55fe77d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UgKkDPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUgKkDPL.jpg&h=2ca3fea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#推廣時間<br />\n<br />\n各位學員們，希望大家可以幫下手推廣吓我哋呢個channel 除咗叫你哋身邊嘅朋友一齊操之外仲可以將我哋既文宣印出嚟畀你哋附近嘅黃店貼出嚟等多啲人一齊操fit 自己<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n從來都唔係一個口號而係一個行動<br />\n<br />\nTg link:<a href=\"https://t.me/ekrtc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fekrtc&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=3e4d1114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ekrtc</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yOcVsKw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOcVsKw.jpg&h=a3912e14&s={SIZE}\" 